Masters, Slaves, and Piconets


Bluetooth networks (piconets) use a master/slave model. Master talk to slave. Slave not master.

Address

48-bit unique address, BD_ADDR. 24 MSBs is Organization Unique Indentifier (OUI)

Name

A

Profile

- Serial Port Profile (SPP): RS232 over the air! the profile that I need!
- Human Interface Device (HID)
- Hands-Free Profile (HFP) and Headset Profile (HSP)
- Advanced Audio Distribution Profile (A2DP)
- A/V Remote Control Profile (AVRCP)

Version:

v4.0 : classic, high speed and low energy. BLE 1Mbps


